{"type":"message","id":"43e59f4a","parentId":"2e33e8dc","timestamp":"2026-02-28T09:30:18.336Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3ea3b8a5b1ec457db46a2d0b","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"29637\tOPEN\tTelegram group messages not received after upgrade to 2026.2.24+\t\t2026-02-28T09:28:58Z\n29636\tOPEN\tFeishu proxy env precedence test fails on Windows (case-insensitive env vars)\t\t2026-02-28T09:27:55Z\n29632\tOPEN\t[Bug]: Duplicate feishu plugin causes pairing failure after v2026.2.26 upgrade\tbug\t2026-02-28T09:24:51Z\n29626\tOPEN\t[Bug] Telegram bot-to-bot @mention not detected by telegram-auto-reply\tbug\t2026-02-28T09:16:21Z\n29624\tOPEN\t[Bug]: Telegram bot can not send image back.\tbug\t2026-02-28T09:15:10Z\n29623\tOPEN\tBug: Rolling log file uses incorrect date in filename (UTC vs local timezone)\t\t2026-02-28T09:13:15Z\n29622\tOPEN\t[Bug]: feishu bot infinite loop pairing\tbug\t2026-02-28T09:18:39Z\n29618\tOPEN\tfix(agents): stripThoughtSignatures modifies Anthropic thinking blocks, causing API rejection\t\t2026-02-28T09:06:47Z\n29617\tOPEN\tMedia parser: accept `MEDIA :` directives with whitespace around colon\t\t2026-02-28T09:05:39Z\n29611\tOPEN\t[Bug]: Browser tool connection is unstable and drops immediately after being established\tbug\t2026-02-28T08:46:01Z"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":537,"aggregated":"29637\tOPEN\tTelegram group messages not received after upgrade to 2026.2.24+\t\t2026-02-28T09:28:58Z\n29636\tOPEN\tFeishu proxy env precedence test fails on Windows (case-insensitive env vars)\t\t2026-02-28T09:27:55Z\n29632\tOPEN\t[Bug]: Duplicate feishu plugin causes pairing failure after v2026.2.26 upgrade\tbug\t2026-02-28T09:24:51Z\n29626\tOPEN\t[Bug] Telegram bot-to-bot @mention not detected by telegram-auto-reply\tbug\t2026-02-28T09:16:21Z\n29624\tOPEN\t[Bug]: Telegram bot can not send image back.\tbug\t2026-02-28T09:15:10Z\n29623\tOPEN\tBug: Rolling log file uses incorrect date in