{"type":"message","id":"41d12afd","parentId":"3797cfb0","timestamp":"2026-03-02T01:20:08.705Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Coding Agent\n\n现在我找到了问题所在！问题出现在 `pi-embedded-subscribe.ts` 文件中，特别是在处理流式传输和块回复的逻辑中。\n\n根据issue描述，问题是在Codex模型输出原始函数调用语法（如 `assistant to=functions.*`）时，这些内容没有被过滤就直接发送到用户聊天中。\n\n让我分析关键代码：\n\n1. **`emitBlockChunk` 函数** - 这是发送块回复的地方\n2. **`stripBlockTags` 函数** - 这是用来清理thinking和final标签的\n3. **缺少对函数调用语法的过滤**\n\n问题在于当前的代码只处理了 `<thinking>` 和 `<final>` 标签，但没有处理OpenAI函数调用的原始语法 `assistant to=functions.*`。\n\n让我创建修复方案。我需要在 `emitBlockChunk` 函数中添加一个过滤器来移除这些函数调用语法。\n\n首先，让我创建一个新的工具文件来处理这个过滤：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e508cf694d934a5c8c8f69a5","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"src/agents/pi-embedded-sanitize.ts","content":"/**\n * Sanitizes model output to remove raw function-call syntax and hallucinated tokens.\n * This prevents leakage of internal model wire format into user-facing channels.\n */\n\nconst FUNCTION_CALL_LEAK_RE = /assistant to=functions\\.\\S+/g;\nconst HALLUCINATED_SPAM_PATTERNS = [\n  // Chinese lottery/gambling spam patterns commonly hallucinated by Codex\n  /体育彩票|北京赛车群|大发分分彩|天天中彩票网"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"src/agents/pi-embedded-sanitize.ts\", \"content\": \"/**\\n * Sanitizes model output to remove raw function-call syntax and hallucinated tokens.\\n * This prevents leakage of internal model wire format into user-facing channels.\\n */\\n\\nconst FUNCTION_CALL_LEAK_RE = /assistant to=functions\\\\.\\\\S+/g;\\nconst HALLUCINATED_SPAM_PATTERNS = [\\n  // Chinese lottery/gambling spam patterns commonly hallucinated by Codex\\n  /体育彩票|北京赛车群|大发分分彩|天天中彩票网"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1772414357665,"errorMessage":"Output data may contain inappropriate content. Fo