{"type":"message","id":"e30e5223","parentId":"91153d0a","timestamp":"2026-03-02T01:39:10.696Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Coding Agent\n\n我是**Coding Agent**，专门负责开源代码贡献和bug修复！\n\n关于您提到的issue #30441（Codex子代理泄露原始函数调用语法的问题），我已经在分析代码了。让我继续深入查找问题根源。\n\n从我查看的代码来看，问题可能出现在消息流处理的某个环节。让我检查一下输出过滤和清理的逻辑。\n\n根据issue描述，问题是在子代理公告输出和流式传输路径中没有对畸形的函数调用模式进行清理。建议的解决方案是添加一个正则表达式过滤器：\n\n```javascript\nconst FUNCTION_CALL_LEAK = /assistant to=functions\\.\\S+/g;\nconst sanitized = output.replace(FUNCTION_CALL_LEAK, '').trim();\n```\n\n让我查找在哪里可以添加这个过滤器。看起来最可能的位置是在 `pi-embedded-subscribe.ts` 文件中的消息处理部分，或者在 `subagent-announce.ts` 的输出生成部分。\n\n让我创建修复方案：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_624737fe1d42487dbe49f75a","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"src/agents/subagent-sanitize-output.ts","content":"/**\n * Sanitizes subagent output to prevent function-call syntax leaks and hallucinated content.\n * This addresses issue #30441 where Codex models emit raw function-call wire format\n * mixed with hallucinated tokens (e.g., Chinese spam/gambling phrases).\n */\n\n/**\n * Regular expression to match OpenAI function-call wire format patterns\n * that may leak into user-facing output when models fail to produce structured tool calls.\n */\nconst FUNCTION_CALL_LEAK_PATTERN = /assistant\\s+to=functions\\.\\S+/gi;\n\n/**\n * Additional patterns to catch hallucinated content that commonly appears\n * in Codex model failures (Chinese lottery/gambling spam phrases from training data).\n */\nconst HALLUCINATED_SPAM_PATTERNS = [\n  /体育彩票|北京赛车群|大发分分彩|天天中彩票网|一级a做爰片|大发"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"src/agents/subagent-sanitize-output.ts\", \"content\": \"/**\\n * Sanitizes subagent output to prevent function-call syntax leaks and hallucinated content.\\n * This addresses issue #30441 where Codex models emit raw function-call wire format\\n * mixed with hallucinated tokens (e.g., Chinese spam/gambling phrases).\\n */\\n\\n/**\\n * Regular expression to match OpenAI function-call wire format patterns\\n * that may leak into user-facing output when models fail to produce structured tool calls.\\n */\\nconst FUNCTION_CALL_LEAK_PATTERN = /assistant\\\\s+to=functions\\\\.\\\\S+/gi;\\n\\n/**\\n * Additional patterns to catch hallucinated content that commonly appears\\n * in Codex model failures (Chinese lottery/gambling spam phrases from training data).\\n */\\nconst HALLUCINATED_SPAM_PATTERNS = [\\n  /体育彩票|北京赛车群|大发分分彩|天天中彩票网|一级a做爰片|大发"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1772415497193,"errorMessage":"Output data may contain inappropriate content. For details, see: https://help.aliyun.com/zh/model-studio/error-code#inappropriate-content"}}
