{"type":"message","id":"22ba20b4","parentId":"1040ed8a","timestamp":"2026-03-02T01:53:09.694Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Coding Agent\n\n好的！我暂停当前的bug修复工作。\n\n**当前进度总结：**\n- ✅ 已识别 **Issue #30441**: \"Codex subagent emits raw function-call syntax and hallucinated tokens to user chat\"\n- ✅ 已创建feature分支 `feature/codex-function-call-sanitization`\n- ✅ 已分析相关代码文件（`subagent-announce.ts`, `pi-embedded-subscribe.ts`, `pi-embedded-subscribe.handlers.messages.ts`）\n- ⏸️ 正在定位具体的函数调用语法泄露点\n\n**下一步需要做的：**\n1. 在消息输出路径中添加函数调用语法清理过滤器\n2. 实现正则表达式过滤 `assistant to=functions.*` 模式\n3. 添加测试用例验证修复效果\n\n如果您需要我继续这个修复，或者想处理其他issue，请告诉我！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":124068,"output":195,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124263,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772416381524}}
{"type":"message","id":"03ba0983","parentId":"22ba20b4","timestamp":"2026-03-02T01:53:19.838Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-03-02 09:53 GMT+8] 先更新你对应功能的技能skills，明白工作流程，解决某个issue或者bug： 1，需要先在fork项目切到main，sync fork，确保跟官方master的代码保持一致 2，然后新建一个解决问题的feature，在这个feature分支上开发代码测试 3，提交代码到feature分支，按社区规范向官方项目提交PR。"}],"timestamp":1772416399835}}
