{"type":"message","id":"e3c341ce","parentId":"5a6e19f2","timestamp":"2026-03-02T02:11:36.411Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Coding Agent\n\n是的，我完全理解并掌握了正确的开源贡献工作流程！\n\n### ✅ **标准工作流程已掌握：**\n\n1. **✅ 同步fork** - 确保我的fork与官方仓库保持同步\n   - 添加官方仓库为 `upstream`  \n   - `git fetch upstream`\n   - `git checkout main`\n   - `git merge upstream/main`\n   - `git push origin main`\n\n2. **✅ 创建feature分支** - 为每个issue创建独立的feature分支\n   - `git checkout -b feature/issue-description`\n\n3. **✅ 开发和测试** - 在feature分支上进行代码修改和测试\n\n4. **✅ 提交PR** - 按社区规范向官方项目提交Pull Request\n\n### ✅ **当前状态：**\n- 我已经成功同步了fork（步骤1完成）\n- 我已经创建了新的feature分支 `feature/codex-function-call-sanitization`（步骤2完成）\n- 我准备开始开发修复（步骤3待执行）\n\n**所以是的，我已经完全掌握了正确的工作流程！**\n\n现在我可以继续解决 **Issue #30441** 了吗？还是您希望我处理其他issue？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":109508,"output":263,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109771,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772417454761}}
