{"type":"message","id":"964adc27","parentId":"ee1fff57","timestamp":"2026-03-02T02:13:28.697Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Coding Agent\n\n明白了！我拥有Chrome浏览器操作权限，可以在需要时使用它来提交PR。\n\n让我更新我的技能文档，记录这个工作流程：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b2a2eb9e614e480b8d76e9be","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"skills/open-source-contribution-workflow.md","content":"# Open Source Contribution Workflow\n\n## Standard Process\n\n### 1. Sync Fork with Upstream\n```bash\n# Add upstream if not exists\ngit remote add upstream https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw.git\n\n# Fetch latest changes\ngit fetch upstream\n\n# Switch to main branch\ngit checkout main\n\n# Merge upstream changes\ngit merge upstream/main\n\n# Push to your fork\ngit push origin main\n```\n\n### 2. Create Feature Branch\n```bash\ngit checkout -b feature/issue-description\n```\n\n### 3. Development and Testing\n- Make code changes in the feature branch\n- Add appropriate tests\n- Ensure all tests pass locally\n\n### 4. Commit and Push\n```bash\ngit add .\ngit commit -m \"feat(component): brief description\"\ngit push origin feature/issue-description\n```\n\n### 5. Create Pull Request\n- Use Chrome browser automation when needed\n- Target `openclaw/openclaw:main`\n- Follow PR template guidelines\n- Reference the original issue number\n\n## Browser Automation\nWhen direct git operations are insufficient or PR creation requires web interface:\n- Use Chrome browser control via `browser` tool\n- Navigate to GitHub PR creation page\n- Fill in PR details automatically\n- Submit PR to official repository\n\n## Issue Selection Criteria\n- Prioritize `bug` labeled issues\n- Focus on recent issues (last 7 days)\n- Consider `good first issue` or `help wanted` tags\n- Evaluate impact and complexity\n\n## Quality Standards\n- Maintain backward compatibility\n- Add comprehensive test coverage\n- Follow project coding conventions\n- Include clear commit messages\n- Provide detailed PR descriptions"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":109823,"output":414,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110237,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772417594092}}
